You can have your fun and eat it, too.

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:56.400
This morning, we were regular fifth graders.

00:02:56.400 --> 00:02:57.400
Now we're heroes.

00:02:57.400 --> 00:03:00.400
It all started when we were separated from our class

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:01.400
