00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:03.400
We were off goofing around when we realized...

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:04.400
Wait!

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:05.400
What if it was our bus?

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:07.400
We knew if we missed our bus, we'd be toast.

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:11.400
Once we saw our bus, we figured we were aces.

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:12.400
We were wrong.

00:03:12.400 --> 00:03:14.400
How come we don't know anyone on this bus?

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:15.400
Because that's our bus.

00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:17.400
What bus are you boys supposed to be on?

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:19.400
The one that's going to McDonald's.

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:24.060
