When summer starts,

00:03:41.070 --> 00:03:43.070
you can't wait to get out the suntan lotion,

00:03:43.070 --> 00:03:45.070
the charcoal, the volleyball net.

00:03:45.070 --> 00:03:46.070
But by the end of the summer,

00:03:46.070 --> 00:03:48.070
