00:03:49.070 --> 00:03:51.070
The mosquitoes think you're lunch meat

00:03:51.070 --> 00:03:53.070
and if you see one more roasted wiener,

00:03:53.070 --> 00:03:54.070
you're cute.

00:03:55.070 --> 00:03:57.670
Or how about that time

00:03:57.670 --> 00:03:59.670
you're really sick and tired of one look?

00:03:59.670 --> 00:04:03.520
Something really cool comes along.

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:06.520
Then there are things that never change.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:08.520
Things you can always count on.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.520
The way school smells,

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:11.520
the way will socks feel itchy.

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:13.520
And then of course,

00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:15.520
they're your grandparents.

00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:17.520
Talk about dependable.

00:04:17.520 --> 00:04:18.520
They're always glad to see you.

00:04:18.520 --> 00:04:20.520
They always take your side.

00:04:20.520 --> 00:04:22.520
And they always think you're the smartest,

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:23.520
cutest kid in the world.

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:24.520
Sometimes it's hard to believe

00:04:24.520 --> 00:04:26.520
