00:04:26.520 --> 00:04:28.520
And you want to know the best thing about grandparents?

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:29.520
They're coming today.

00:04:30.520 --> 00:05:26.960
Before my dad's parents get here.

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:27.960
It's a big deal.

00:05:27.960 --> 00:05:29.960
They're 40th wedding anniversary.

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:30.960
We're throwing a party.

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:32.960
And I get to DJ.

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:33.960
Let's see.

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:35.960
Would Count Basie segue into Fouchnickens?

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:37.960
Well, the party's not till the end of the week.

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:39.960
So I've got time to think about it.

00:05:39.960 --> 00:05:40.960
Besides,

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:41.960
I've got a lot more to do

00:05:41.960 --> 00:05:43.960
