00:05:43.960 --> 00:05:44.960
I'm all set.

00:05:44.960 --> 00:05:46.960
Cards for gin rummy,

00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:47.960
Mark's Brothers movies,

00:05:47.960 --> 00:05:48.960
board games.

