Sounds pretty tame,

00:05:49.960 --> 00:05:51.960
but they're not the most active people in the world.

00:05:51.960 --> 00:05:52.960
Like last year

00:05:52.960 --> 00:05:54.960
when we had our own spring training in the backyard.

00:05:55.960 --> 00:06:00.160
And how about our trip to the lake?

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:05.160
Talk about the one that got away.

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:08.800
Then there was my sixth birthday

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:10.800
when we tried to play hide and seek.

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:12.800
Wasn't too tough to find them.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:17.040
Sure, I've outgrown some of this stuff,

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:18.040
but they like it,

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:19.040
and I like them.

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:21.040
Hi, Sam.

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:23.040
Did you get them?

00:06:24.040 --> 00:06:25.040
Sure, I got them.

00:06:26.040 --> 00:06:27.040
Sort of.

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:28.040
Sort of?

00:06:28.040 --> 00:06:29.040
Sam,

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:31.040
you don't sort of get Pearl Jam tickets.

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:32.040
You either get them or you don't.

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:33.040
You got them.

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:34.040
Didn't you?

