00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:41.040
Well, that's how Pearl Jam's going to look to us.

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:43.040
Little.

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:46.040
Bro, are in the second balcony?

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:48.040
I thought the music editor owed your dad a favor.

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:49.040
These are nosebleed seats.

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:52.040
Well, they are for free.

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:53.040
And it is Pearl Jam.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:54.040
So we're on?

00:06:54.040 --> 00:06:55.040
We're on.

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:58.040
Hey, what's all this stuff for?

00:06:58.040 --> 00:07:00.040
Just stuff I'm going to do with my grandparents.

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:02.040
Wow.

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:04.040
I never plan to do anything with my grandpa.

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:06.040
He just rests all the time.

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:07.040
It's like a hobby.

00:07:07.040 --> 00:07:08.040
He eats breakfast,

00:07:08.040 --> 00:07:09.040
