00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:58.040
to make sure I don't swallow any of the small pieces.

00:07:58.040 --> 00:07:59.040
Come on, you're exaggerating.

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:00.040
Oh, yeah?

00:08:00.040 --> 00:08:01.040
Last time they were here,

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:04.040
they took me to see Rafi, Aethro Center.

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:05.040
Hmm.

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:06.040
Aethro for Rafi.

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:08.040
Second balcony for Pearl Jam.

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:10.040
What's wrong with this picture?

00:08:10.040 --> 00:08:16.080
I can't believe you're making pot roast, Mom.

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:18.080
Believe me, it wasn't my idea,

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:21.080
