00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:23.080
It's just too bad, Grandma and Grandpa

00:08:23.080 --> 00:08:26.080
haven't discovered the benefits of health foods.

00:08:26.080 --> 00:08:27.080
I just have to suffer through it

00:08:27.080 --> 00:08:28.080
and pretend we like it.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.080
Yes!

00:08:30.080 --> 00:08:32.080
Where are they?

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:33.080
They're late.

00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:35.080
They're never late, but they're late.

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:37.080
Marshall, I'm sure they're fine.

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:38.080
And so is the pot roast.

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:39.080
I've already seasoned it with herbs.

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:40.080
I think they'll like it.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.080
Well, let's make sure.

00:08:41.080 --> 00:08:42.080
Marshall?

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:43.080
Janet, can we just do this?

00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:45.080
I do not want to sit through two hours

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.080
and my parents telling us the right way to make pot roast.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.080
Chill out, Dad.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:50.080
It's just beef.

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:52.080
Well, you try telling them that.

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:54.080
If you're going to get this upset over a pot roast,

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:56.080
how are you going to handle their anniversary?

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:58.080
You're right.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:08:59.080
I know.

00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:02.610
It just doesn't matter what I do.

00:09:02.610 --> 00:09:04.610
They find it too radical.

00:09:04.610 --> 00:09:06.610
When I had my hair long, they wanted it short.

00:09:06.610 --> 00:09:08.610
My major in architecture, they wanted an accountant.

00:09:08.610 --> 00:09:10.610
I had my own rock and roll band

00:09:10.610 --> 00:09:13.610
