00:09:13.610 --> 00:09:15.610
And forget about politics.

00:09:15.610 --> 00:09:17.610
Well, they are a little straight-laced.

00:09:17.610 --> 00:09:19.610
I just wish they would loosen up a little.

00:09:19.610 --> 00:09:20.610
They're so conservative.

00:09:20.610 --> 00:09:21.610
My kind of people.

00:09:21.610 --> 00:09:23.610
Your kind of people are slimy with fins.

00:09:23.610 --> 00:09:24.610
Slug.

00:09:24.610 --> 00:09:25.610
Come on back.

00:09:25.610 --> 00:09:26.610
Hold it.

00:09:26.610 --> 00:09:28.610
There will be none of that.

00:09:28.610 --> 00:09:30.610
For the week my parents are here, there will be peace and quiet.

00:09:30.610 --> 00:09:32.610
Not too much excitement.

00:09:32.610 --> 00:09:34.610
Not too much stress.

00:09:34.610 --> 00:09:37.610
Well, they'll probably be worn out from the trip anyway.

00:09:39.610 --> 00:09:40.610
Finally.

00:09:40.610 --> 00:09:41.610
All right.

00:09:41.610 --> 00:09:42.610
Okay.

00:09:42.610 --> 00:09:43.610
They're here.

00:09:43.610 --> 00:09:44.610
Okay.

00:09:44.610 --> 00:09:45.610
Is everything okay?

00:09:45.610 --> 00:09:46.610
Is the meat okay?

00:09:46.610 --> 00:09:53.120
Do I look okay?

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:54.120
Uh-huh.

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:55.120
Hey, hey.

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.120
Now remember what I said.

00:09:56.120 --> 00:09:57.120
Let's just take it nice and slow.

00:09:57.120 --> 00:10:13.710
I know everybody's excited, but...

00:10:13.710 --> 00:10:14.710
Give us a hug.

00:10:14.710 --> 00:10:16.710
Get over here, slugger.

00:10:16.710 --> 00:10:17.710
Um, where were you?

00:10:17.710 --> 00:10:19.710
Yes, we were beginning to worry.

00:10:19.710 --> 00:10:21.710
Nana, Papa, don't you want to sit down?

00:10:21.710 --> 00:10:22.710
Oh, no, no.

00:10:22.710 --> 00:10:23.710
I'll tense up.

00:10:23.710 --> 00:10:24.710
I have to work out.

00:10:24.710 --> 00:10:25.710
It's best to keep moving.

00:10:25.710 --> 00:10:26.710
Stay loose.

00:10:26.710 --> 00:10:27.710
Work out?

